What you need to know:  Exchequers beat Kenya Police 4-1, United States International University of Africa (USIU-A) 2-0 before they wrapped up their home matches with a 4-2 win over StrathmoreIn an earlier match played at the same venue, Kenya Police bounced back to winning ways with a 4-1 win against compatriots USIU-AThe tournament takes a break on Tuesday before action resumes on Wednesday at the same venue